ActEmployment Insurance Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS in order to ensure a better reflection of regional labour market conditions in the territories, while also recognizing differences in labour market realities between capital and non-capital areas in the Yukon, the Northwest Territories, Nunavut and Prince Edward Island.
